Author: empoweredaritay
Text: ugh same. I've avoided going out because I can't deal with it anymore and I always try to find outfits that make me look thinner but nothing works and I give up. I can't even go out without body checking like every 5 minutes and god knows if I drink and get the drunchies/want to eat something I'll have a melt down :(
